{"tid":601263,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸人真係好on9","createTime":"2018-03-22T05:39:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T09:05:34.000Z","uid":165349,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"260a78a46e2f0b99cfc907bcf4fb8ec30c297ea4","tid":601263,"uid":165349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T05:39:34.000Z","msg":"話說放lunch去公司附近茶餐廳食飯<br />\n好多人排隊比錢（收銀係門口）本身都好擠迫<br />\n有個著西裝睇落幾敦厚既男人 企左係張檯隔離 塞住個通道唔知做乜9<br />\n咁我就越過佢 入去有waiter帶位啦（利申有好多位 但係搭檯的）<br />\n點知個西裝友即刻衝出黎 用啲大陸口音廣東話鬧 唔洗排隊呀你？<br />\n我同個waiter不約而同對望而笑<br />\nwaiter話 咁你先囉<br />\n我就話 你入去先囉 咁多位<br />\n<br />\n其實大陸人真係on9 咁鍾意衝出黎柒<br />\n可能黎香港唔知係可以自己入去坐/搵人帶位/興搭檯 係都要on99企係度等<br />\n唔入鄉隨俗 唔適應香港都算 仲要唔知自己柒 覺得係人地錯 鬧番人轉頭 真係得啖笑<br />\n諗深層佢都應該多謝我 如果唔係佢可能排都聽朝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2faef2769f0c7d8179c2d9e661dd55ac94d30dc","tid":601263,"uid":2507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T05:42:16.000Z","msg":"唔係你佢應該lunch都冇得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"470f3d34e622d6fe4438814121d5b10863bf007e","tid":601263,"uid":165349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2faef2769f0c7d8179c2d9e661dd55ac94d30dc","tid":601263,"uid":2507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T05:42:16.000Z","msg":"唔係你佢應該lunch都冇得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T05:51:05.000Z","msg":"可能心諗點解冇人黎帶位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"562e92221df30a04e4a711f749904606a3c2a852","tid":601263,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T06:35:29.000Z","msg":"你又會讓佢咁 on9，直接屌返佢啦"},{"pid":"b74518951d8134e56818d3eb39b72500f01ab5ee","tid":601263,"uid":165349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"562e92221df30a04e4a711f749